<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 00:51:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾对中国“单方面”改变台湾海峡航线感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-angered-unilateral-china-change-taiwan-strait-flight-path-2024-01-31/</link><description>台湾政府对中国“单方面”改变靠近台湾海峡敏感中线的飞行路线表示愤怒，称这似乎是故意试图改变现状，以可能采取军事手段。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 00:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-angered-unilateral-china-change-taiwan-strait-flight-path-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>尽管存在分歧，欧盟贸易主管仍将继续推进美国电池矿物谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-trade-chief-press-with-us-battery-minerals-talks-despite-differences-2024-01-30/</link><description>欧盟最高贸易官员周二表示，美国和欧盟周二未能就关键电池矿物达成贸易协议，但誓言将继续推进谈判，以建立一个跨大西洋的矿物和其他零部件市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:51:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-trade-chief-press-with-us-battery-minerals-talks-despite-differences-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局局长：基辅今年面临艰苦战斗，美国援助流动至关重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/cia-chief-kyiv-faces-tough-battle-this-year-us-aid-flows-vital-2024-01-30/</link><description>中央情报局局长比尔伯恩斯周二表示，2024年乌克兰可能会面临与俄罗斯作战的艰难一年，他认为切断美国对基辅的援助将是一个“历史性的”错误。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/cia-chief-kyiv-faces-tough-battle-this-year-us-aid-flows-vital-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：中国采购经理人指数、美联储声明将测试增长前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-30/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 21:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>星巴克因中东冲突下调销售预期，警告第二季度疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-misses-quarterly-sales-estimates-2024-01-30/</link><description>由于以色列与哈马斯战争损害了其中东业务，星巴克周二下调了年度销售预期，同时警告称，一月份需求疲软和中国复苏缓慢可能会削弱其第二季度业绩。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 21:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-misses-quarterly-sales-estimates-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>雪佛龙将哈萨克斯坦石油改道至非洲周边的亚洲 - 消息来源，伦敦证券交易所集团数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chevron-reroutes-kazakh-oil-asia-around-africa-sources-lseg-data-2024-01-30/</link><description>据三位行业消息人士和伦敦证券交易所集团船舶跟踪数据显示，雪佛龙正在将哈萨克斯坦的 CPC Blend 石油货物沿着非洲好望角而不是通过红海运往亚洲，以避免也门胡塞武装发动袭击的风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 18:24:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chevron-reroutes-kazakh-oil-asia-around-africa-sources-lseg-data-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车需求放缓，行业痛苦加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/industry-pain-abounds-electric-car-demand-hits-slowdown-2024-01-30/</link><description>尽管汽车制造商对电动汽车的未来需求下了很大的赌注，但近期的全球经济放缓正在带来痛苦。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 15:43:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/industry-pain-abounds-electric-car-demand-hits-slowdown-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>博尔顿在新回忆录介绍中称特朗普“不适合”担任总统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bolton-excoriates-trump-fresh-introduction-his-memoir-2024-01-30/</link><description>美国前国家安全顾问约翰·博尔顿在周二发布的新版回忆录中痛斥前总统唐纳德·特朗普是一个完全自私的人，他会惩罚私人敌人并安抚对手俄罗斯和中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:07:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bolton-excoriates-trump-fresh-introduction-his-memoir-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>IMF称全球“软着陆”在望，上调2024年增长前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-says-global-soft-landing-sight-raises-2024-economic-growth-outlook-2024-01-30/</link><description>国际货币基金组织上调了美国和中国的前景展望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-says-global-soft-landing-sight-raises-2024-economic-growth-outlook-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织上调亚洲增长预测，警告中国风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imf-revises-up-asias-growth-forecast-warns-china-risk-2024-01-30/</link><description>国际货币基金组织 (IMF) 周二预计亚洲新兴经济体今年将增长 5.2%，较 2023 年有所放缓，但因中国经济增长强于预期而上调了三个月前的预测。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imf-revises-up-asias-growth-forecast-warns-china-risk-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>中美芬太尼合作北京期待“正能量”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-cooperate-fentanyl-beijing-hopes-positive-energy-2024-01-30/</link><description>周二，美国和中国成立了联合禁毒工作组，这是自 2019 年底以来两个超级大国双边关系恶化之前首次公开合作应对芬太尼泛滥。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:08:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-cooperate-fentanyl-beijing-hopes-positive-energy-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>台湾空军展示潜猎预警能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-air-force-shows-off-its-sub-hunting-early-warning-prowess-2024-01-30/</link><description>周二，台湾空军展示了全副武装的潜艇猎手以及预警和控制飞机，展示了它如何监视中国声称拥有主权的岛屿周围的天空和水域。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-air-force-shows-off-its-sub-hunting-early-warning-prowess-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商宁德时代预计2023年盈利增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-battery-giant-catl-expects-2023-earnings-jump-by-up-48-2024-01-30/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 电池巨头宁德时代 (CATL) 周二预计 2023 年净利润增长高达 48.1%，由于需求放缓和激烈竞争，该公司的增长大幅低于上年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-battery-giant-catl-expects-2023-earnings-jump-by-up-48-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：退款燃料、大型股更新、中国陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-30/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>德国将批准欧盟计划中的人工智能法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/germany-will-approve-eus-planned-ai-act-sources-2024-01-30/</link><description>在负责数字问题的部长表示已经达成妥协后，德国将批准欧盟开创性的人工智能法案。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 10:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/germany-will-approve-eus-planned-ai-act-sources-2024-01-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>